利益，而竊佔他人之不動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/ULDM/110%2c%e6%b8%af%e7%b0%a1%2c148%2c20211028%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"ULDM,110,港簡,148,20211028,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"港簡","JNO":"148","JDATE":"20211028","JTITLE":"竊盜"}